---
import CallToAction from './CallToAction.astro';
---

<aside>
	<div class="deco deco-left">✦</div>
	<div class="deco deco-right">✿</div>
	<h2>ご相談・お問い合わせはこちらから ♡</h2>
	<p>ただお話したいだけでも大歓迎です！</p>
	<CallToAction href="mailto:yumikofurukawa64@gmail.com">
		メッセージを送る ✉
	</CallToAction>
</aside>

<style>
	aside {
		position: relative;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 2rem;
		border-top: 2px dashed var(--accent-light);
		border-bottom: 2px dashed var(--accent-light);
		padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
		background: var(--gradient-subtle);
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.deco {
		position: absolute;
		font-size: 5rem;
		opacity: 0.12;
		color: var(--accent-regular);
		pointer-events: none;
		line-height: 1;
	}

	.deco-left {
		top: 1rem;
		left: 2rem;
		transform: rotate(-15deg);
	}

	.deco-right {
		bottom: 1rem;
		right: 2rem;
		transform: rotate(15deg);
	}

	h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		text-align: center;
		background: var(--gradient-accent);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
	}

	p {
		color: var(--gray-300);
		text-align: center;
		font-size: var(--text-md);
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		aside {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
			padding: 7rem 5rem;
			gap: 2.5rem;
		}

		h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-3xl);
		}
	}
</style>
